msgid ""
"Menu entries for executing applications are defined by the <c>[exec]</c>\n"
"element. You can define an entry, either under the <c>[begin]</c> definition\n"
"(the menu root), or between a <c>[submenu]</c> and its corresponding\n"
"<c>[end]</c> line (submenu definitions), for example:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <guide><chapter><section><body><pre>
#: en/fluxbox-config.xml:629
#, no-wrap
msgid "Defining new menu entries"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><pre>
#: en/fluxbox-config.xml:630
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# Custom fluxbox menu\n"
"[begin] (Fluxbox)\n"
"  <comment>(...)</comment>\n"
"  [exec] (XTerm White on Black) {xterm -ls -fg white -bg black}\n"
"  <comment>(...)</comment>\n"
"  [submenu] (More terminals)\n"
"    [exec] (Aterm default) {aterm}\n"
"    [exec] (Rxvt default) {rxvt}\n"
"  [end]\n"
"  <comment>(...)</comment>\n"
"[end]\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><p>
#: en/fluxbox-config.xml:644
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"The root menu definition begins with the <c>[begin]</c> tag, followed by its\n"
"name, between parentheses and ends with its corresponding <c>[end]</c> tag. All\n"
"the menu commands (called here, tags) are enclosed by square brackets, menu\n"
"names will be enclosed between parentheses and the actual commands are enclosed\n"
"between braces. Comments are allowed in this file, for lines beginning with\n"
"<c>#</c>.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><p>
#: en/fluxbox-config.xml:653
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"In the example shown above, the first <c>[exec]</c> line defines a new entry\n"
"named \"XTerm White on Black\", which will execute the <c>xterm -ls -fg white -bg\n"
"black</c> as if from a command line. Next is a submenu which is defined using\n"
"the <c>[submenu]</c> tag, and after that a section called \"More terminals\",\n"
"with two more <c>[exec]</c> commands. Any submenu definition must have its\n"
"corresponding <c>[end]</c> tag.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><p>
#: en/fluxbox-config.xml:662
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"There are other menu commands that you can use in your\n"
"<path>~/.fluxbox/menu</path> file. Please read the <uri\n"
"link=\"http://fluxbox.org/docbook.php\">official documentation</uri>\n"
"available online for more information.\n"
msgstr ""

